<section>
	<h3>p-button-group 的使用方法</h3>
	<p>目前主要接受的属性有 value / type / vertical ；</p>
	<p>接受的方法为 onChange</p>
	<p>其中，value 为 子button 中的 active 的值</p>
	<p>type 只能接受 ‘radio’</p>
	<p>vertical 默认为 false，通过
		{{#p-button value=vertical type="default" onClick=(action 'changeVertical' )}}changeVertical{{/p-button}}
		可将其变为垂直排列。
	</p>
	{{#p-button-group value=buttonGroupValue type="radio" vertical=vertical onChange=(action (mut buttonGroupValue)) as |bg|}}
		{{!-- {{#p-button-group value=buttonGroupValue type="radio" onChange=(action 'changeValue') as |bg|}} --}}
		{{#bg.button type="default" value=1}}1{{/bg.button}}
		{{#bg.button type="default" value=2}}second button long long long{{/bg.button}}
		{{#bg.button type="default" value=3}}3{{/bg.button}}
	{{/p-button-group}}
	You selected: {{buttonGroupValue}}!
</section>